# 🍔 Tomato - Food Delivery Website

**Tomato** is a simple and responsive food delivery website created using only **HTML** and **CSS**. This project showcases the UI design of a food ordering platform, including various sections like a homepage, offers, menu, order tracking, and about us.

## 🔧 Technologies Used

- **HTML5** – Markup structure of the website  
- **CSS3** – Styling and layout (Internal/External CSS)

## 📂 Project Structure

```bash
Tomato-Food-Delivery/
├── index.html           # Homepage
├── offers.html          # Offers page
├── menu.html            # Menu items with prices
├── order.html           # Order tracking page
├── about.html           # About the company
├── contact.html         # Contact page
├── header.html          # Reusable header (PHP include)
├── footer.html          # Reusable footer (PHP include)
├── css/
│   └── style.css        # Main stylesheet
└── images/              # Food and UI images
